    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2D indie game with traditional animations and high difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The prequel to Templar 2.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[img][/img]<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337340/extras/bedf0b5d6ed73d9ccdb7ffebf2e53fc6.poster.avif?t=1736915375\" width=414 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337340/extras/bedf0b5d6ed73d9ccdb7ffebf2e53fc6.webm?t=1736915375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337340/extras/bedf0b5d6ed73d9ccdb7ffebf2e53fc6.mp4?t=1736915375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the true story of Ruy, the last Templar knight. Disappeared on a mission, he is now the only hope left for a world plunged into chaos caused by the red plague, where every dead person becomes a terrible demon...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-30 Levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Potions and objects that will allow you to advance in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A soundtrack as terrifying as it is epic and rocking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Classic 2D graphics with traditional animation.</p>",
